OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Facross the south mostly fading during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Otherwise dry, with
OL,8,Fvariable amounts of cloud. Cloudier in
OL,9,Fthe north, with patchy rain sinking
OL,10,Fsouth across parts of Scotland. Fresh
OL,11,Fnortherly winds developing in the
OL,12,Fnorth, feeling cooler here.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FDry for many, with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,16,FShowery outbreaks of rain continuing
OL,17,Fto push south across northern areas.
OL,18,FBrighter conditions follow as colder
OL,19,Fair arrives.
